reviewText: It's not the "amateur" homegrown footage that is all over the place these days. Like the amateur videos, these scenes appear to be shot inside homes and not on a lavish set, even though the cameras, lights and models are clearly professionals. The models are film stars from Europe and I would say the give performances that rival the best of them. The title says it all blondes, brunettes, redheads. Most of the models are more on the "busty" side. if you are a breast man, this one is for you!
